--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


Commonly used files for STM32 programs.
This replaces the copter directory.
Files are currently built by the projects which use them.


bootloader.c: Bootloader for UART programming

bootloader.ld: Linker script for the bootloader

main.ld: Linker script for the mane program.

uart_programmer.c: Program the mane program with the bootloader

asm
linux
net
linux.h: make the stm32 look like Linux for porting kernel drivers

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
